---
source: crates/franken-node/tests/cli_subcommand_goldens.rs
---
Trust-card API[PATH] parity surfaces

Usage: franken-node trust-card <COMMAND>

Commands:
  show     Show trust-card details for one extension
  export   Export a trust card in machine-readable form
  list     List trust cards with publisher[PATH] filters
  compare  Compare trust posture between two extensions
  diff     Diff two trust-card versions for the same extension
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
